What is Virtualization and Virtual Machine?

  Virtualization = creating a virtual version of physical resource

How it works: 
• A layer called hypervisor sits on a hardware
• It divides
   o CPU
   o RAM
   o Storage
• Creates multiple virtual systems

What is a Virtual Machine ?
Virtual machine: Software based computer
It has
• OS
• CPU (Virtual CPU)
• RAM (virtual)
• Disk (Virtual)